#: .\item.json
msgid "Survivor's bag"
msgid_plural "Survivor's bags"
msgstr[0] "倖存者的揹包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Survivor's bag"}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"It is a bag that someone had dropped. You can get the items that are "
"included by disassembling."
msgstr "這是一個被人遺落的揹包。你可以通過拆解來獲取其中包含的物品。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Survivor's Lost item"
msgstr "倖存者的遺失物品"

#. ~ Description for Survivor's Lost item
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"You will be able to pick up bags that survivors have dropped from the bushes"
msgstr "你將能從灌木叢中撿到倖存者遺落的揹包"
